\begin_inset Formula $P(N=2)=P(Z_{2}\le\frac{{Ltan\alpha}}{h})=F_{Z_{2}}(\frac{{Ltan\alpha}}{h})$
\end_inset

etc.
 and then calculate expectation of 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

over the pmf.
 
\end_layout

